body.description: Add a modern centerpiece to your home with the Westinghouse Sylvestre Five-Light Chandelier. This sophisticated fixture has refined lines and a shiny brushed nickel finish. Five lights, surrounded by frosted seeded glass shades, provide inviting illumination. Install this chandelier in a foyer, hallway, or dining room. The adjustable chain mount makes it ideal for rooms with high ceilings. Wherever it's placed, this chandelier will provide a graceful accent and welcoming light. Product reference number 62274.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Elegant brushed nickel finish adds sleek contemporary style Three-light frosted seeded cylinder glass shades create a refreshing and inviting light Install in bathroom, powder room, or over a vanity Install wall fixture up or down to suit your needs Ideal for general or task lighting Includes installation instructions and mounting hardware 6227900 Sylvestre Three-Light Interior Wall Fixture, Brushed Nickel Finish With Frosted Seeded Glass Sylvestre Three-Light Indoor Wall Fixture. The crisp, contemporary style of the Westinghouse Sylvestre Three-Light Wall Fixture is a stunning addition to any home. The lovely cylinder glass shades are frosted with a delicate seeded texture that sparkle beautifully. Decorative and functional, this fixture will add an elegant glow over a vanity while providing bright illumination. The Sylvestre is ideal for a bathroom or powder room where task lighting is important. It uses three medium-base light bulbs, 60-watt maximum (not included). You can position the fixture up or down for the look that you desire. This Westinghouse indoor wall fixture is ETL/CETL Listed for safety and is backed by a five-year limited manufacturer's warranty against defects in materials and workmanship. Westinghouse is a trusted, global brand. Westinghouse knows lighting and offers products with exceptional quality, reliability and functionality. Height: 8-1/4 inches Width: 15-3/4 inches Extends from wall: 6-1/4 inches

The Sylvestre features beautiful, frosted seeded glass and a brushed nickel finish. The shades diffuse light beautifully and provide excellent light for tasks and ambience. The Sylvestre three-light wall fixture is a charming addition to any home, and an attractive complement to any decor. Easy to install, the versatile Sylvestre three-light vanity fixture can be positioned up or down to suit your needs. You can hang this three-light wall fixture above a sink with the glass facing upward. Hang the Sylvestre three-light above a vanity with the glass pointing downward for task appropriate downlighting.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 23, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for small area
reviews.reviewText: I used this in my small dining area. If you have a large dining room, it would be too small. For my area, it’s perfect! Looks great and was easy to install

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The new light bulbs fit in this chandelier.
reviews.reviewText: It's in my dining room. I had to replace the one I had because the 'new' light bulbs didn't fit in the glass globes. This one is perfect.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Electrician installed this beautiful chandelier
reviews.reviewText: The self-install instructions showed a different style of chandelier but the electrician had no problem in doing the work. I wouldn't suggest anyone other than an electrician install ANY fixture.It is a beautiful chandelier, made of good materials. It does hang a little crooked, as other reviewers have said. That may have more to do with the way the chain connects, and less to do with any difference in the weight of each "arm".I'll figure a barely-noticable way to weight down the arm that's now highest. Our local hardware store should have something.... but if not, it isn't so crazily out of kilter than most people would notice. It's nonetheless a 4-star very good value and nice addition to the eat-in kitchen.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for the price
reviews.reviewText: Looks beautiful and recommend getting the same brand light bulbs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2017
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Thrilled in all ways with this fixture
reviews.reviewText: Perfect! Simple, modern, un-obstructive and beautiful in our space.Each light takes up to a 60 Watt bulb and if you're worried about it being bright enough, don't....it's very bright.We will either install a dimmer or get lower watt bulbs.Glass covers look great and are much higher quality/thicker than we were expecting.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 25, 2016
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Pleased with this purchase
reviews.reviewText: The package arrived with one broken glass cover. I emailed the company who sent me a replacement. I love the chandelier. It is modern, puts off a great deal of light, and looks great over our kitchen table. For the price, really a great purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 19, 2015
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good product with a defect and product variations
reviews.reviewText: I have this light fixture installed and I like it very much. Simple design compliments simplistic decor of my living room very well.The first product I received had to be returned due to the fact that vertical rod was welded crocked causing the lamps to not level out. Of course, being Amazon, return and replacement was easy and fast.Then, I discovered, first product (original) and the second product (replacement) were not identical. While first one had glass pieces in white without any tint, second one had an obvious green tint. They were also a bit longer. The second one had a threaded rod inside the vertical piece where as first one did not. It doesn't affect functionality but it has (obviously) gone through a design change. Boxing and packing were also different.Installation is very easy and straight forward. 3 wires (including ground) connection and I was done. The actual hanging requires one to open up two of the rings of the chain. As they are made of thick wires, I needed a big wrench and a vice.Overall, it was a very good purchase. I would buy it again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 20, 2014
reviews.reviewText: We ordered four of these. All four arrived intact with no damage. They were easy to install, even though we needed to replace the chain and cord with something longer.They are just as pictured, with one small thing to note: I didn't know what "seeded" glass meant, and I didn't notice from the picture that there are very small circles/ovals in the glass pattern. This isn't a big deal since it's not noticeable, but I would've liked them better with a solid, smooth look.

reviews.reviewTitle: Superior light added 5 led dimable bulbs.
reviews.reviewText: Great light minimal shadows and not stark.

reviews.reviewTitle: Great purchase at a great price.
reviews.reviewText: Wow. Replaced a crappy chandelier with this baby and oh boy does it ever add character to my dining room. Installation was easy, and it is level - not sure why some other folks say it is not level when attached to a level ceiling. I put in some LED lights in there and it will follow me around for years with zero maintenance. I don't think I need anything more than this beauty in any dining room I will inhabit for the next 10 or 15 years. Great purchase and great price.
Very nice style and has worked very well with the dimmer switch installed.
